
Nodes Discovery:

CLI - consul members; 
API - curl localhost:8500/v1/catalog/nodes | python -m json.tool

Services: Webserver - running on 2 servers. 

For Services: curl http://localhost:8500/v1/catalog/services

On Bootstrap Server:

{
"service":{
 "name": "webserver",
 "tags": ["redserver"],
 "port": 80
  }
}

On Server:

{
"service":{
 "name": "webserver",
 "tags": ["redserver"],
 "port": 80
  }
}


For DNS records: dig @localhost -p 8600 webserver.service.consul SRV
		
			curl http://localhost:8500/v1/catalog/service/webserver


Health Checking: curl 'http://localhost:8500/v1/health/service/webserver?passing'
Node:  curl 'http://localhost:8500/v1/health/node/server'